name: defender
display_help: The Defender tends to help their allies, and attack foes, from a distance. The Defender excels at powers that assist friends, but can also hinder their enemies. The Defender is able to attack at quite a range, however, the Defender is not built for hand to hand. They might be able to dodge a few attacks, but the Defender won't last for long.
display_short_help: Helps other Heroes and weakens Foes. Good ranged attacks.
